Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:00:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.46,0:01:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}很抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.49,0:01:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不习惯进自己的房间敲门\NI'm not used to knocking on my own door.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没事\NThat's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}刚才是不是有小孩子的声音\NDid I hear a child's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他爸爸刚送他过来\NHis dad just dropped him by.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我周末照顾他\NI get him on weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}莫纳克打扰到你了吗\NIs Monarch bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没有  他...没事\NNo. He's -- he's -- he's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你认识莱斯利对吗\NSo, you know, uh, Lezley?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.04,0:01:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没人不认识莱斯利\NEverybody knows Lezley...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.14,0:01:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不论他们承认与否\NWhether they want to admit it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:01:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你现在住在那里吗\NYou staying over there now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不是  我\NNo. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.78,0:02:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只有那天晚上在那儿  然后...\NI just went over there the other night and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一直没走\NNever left.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我年轻的时候经常去那里\NI used to go there a lot when I was younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就像成年礼一样\NIt's like a rite of passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}原来之前是那样的\NSo that's what that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你可以喝完啤酒  丹尼尔\NYou can finish your beer, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你想待到什么时候都行\NTake as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你走的时候门会自己锁上\NThe door, it'll lock behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我还是拿着啤酒走吧\NI'll just take it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这个...\NIt's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.64,0:02:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔\NDaniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.06,0:02:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}什么事\NYes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}小心点\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.85,0:02:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你是特别中意我\NWas it me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.53,0:02:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}还是说昨晚陪你的人换谁都可以\Nor could it have been anybody last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有时候...\NSometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.49,0:02:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我做事没有什么理由\NI do things I don't have a good answer for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.26,0:03:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我懂\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}食品超市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.63,0:04:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔·霍顿\NDaniel Holden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}如风般自由\NAs free as the wind blows.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.40,0:04:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}感觉很真实  对吧\NFeels real, don't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}食品超市
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.85,0:05:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}做好准备吧\NFixing to warm up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.61,0:05:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对赖账的人有好处\NIt's good for catfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.59,0:05:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不需要知道怀孕几周了  小泰\NI don't think I need to know how many weeks it was, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.90,0:05:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}爸爸只会是你一个人\NI was there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道  我...\NOh, I-I know. I just --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只是觉得往一根小棒棒上尿尿\NI just thought it was interesting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就能什么都知道\Nyou could pee on a stick now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这很有意思  仅此而已\Nand they'd tell you all that. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}可能将来都能判断\NI mean, one day it'll be able to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是男还是女了呢\Nif it's a boy or girl, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我可不想马上全知道\NI don't think I want to know all that at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都三分钟了\NIt's been three minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不敢看\NI can't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}天哪\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-什么  -你怀孕了\N- What? - You're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真的吗\NReally?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}上面显示已经五周多了\NSays more than five weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}天哪\NOh, my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-我现在可以说吗  -说什么\N- Can I say this right now? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你这个烤炉里正烤着小面包呢\NYou got a bun in the oven right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不  不能这么说\NNo. You can't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好吧  那这么说呢\NAll right. How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.27,0:06:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就说  说"我们怀孕了"\NHow about -- how about "We're pregnant"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不行\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.55,0:06:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那...\NHow about...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}"你怀孕了"  托妮·塔尔博特\N"You're pregnant," Tawney Talbot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你怀孕了\NYou're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.51,0:06:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是的吧\NI guess I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}*千真万确  不可否认*\N*Ain't no lie, can't deny*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}*千真万确  不可否认*\N*Ain't no lie, can't deny*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}*千真万确  不可否认*\N*Ain't no lie, can't deny*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}*千真万确*\N*Ain't no lie*
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不可否认\NCan't deny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我为此祈祷过\NI prayed about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.29,0:06:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真的吗\NYou did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只是祈祷遵循上帝的旨意\NI just prayed that God's will be done, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我就只知道这么做  遵循上帝的旨意\NAnd that's all I knew to do -- his will be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}然后你就怀孕了\NAnd you're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}天哪  你怀孕了\NBy God, you're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是啊  小泰\NI am, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我怀了你的孩子\NWith your baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.37,0:07:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}小泰\NTeddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}什么事  托妮\NYeah, Tawney?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我才刚怀孕不久\NIt's still early.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道  我知道\NI know. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们能先保密吗\NCan we keep it a secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.13,0:07:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就我们两个人先高兴一会儿\NEnjoy it for a little while, just you and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你肯定不会相信\NYou ain't gonna believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}又一棵倒了\NAnother one fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}又一棵\NAnother one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不同的树\NDifferent tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我忘记时间了\NI lost track of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}三天了  丹尼尔\NThree days, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不是给你留言了吗\NI thought I left you a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那是周四早上留的\NThat was Thursday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我和泰德昨晚开车到处找你\NTed and I had to drive around last night looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}很抱歉\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.02,0:08:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我差点就报警了\NI-I almost called the sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我真的不想报警\NI really didn't want to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.27,0:08:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道你不是小孩子  丹尼尔  但是\NI know you're not a teenager, Daniel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但是你也不是那么...\NBut you're also not --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}正常\NNormal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你的人生一直都不太正常\NYour life hasn't been normal,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你又能指望什么呢\Nso how could you expect to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只是想知道你的下落\NLike, I just want to know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好吗  亲爱的\NAll right, sweetheart?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好\NOf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我先走了\NI-I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我得去准备\NI have to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}准备什么\NFor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我要去参加盖恩斯先生的葬礼\NI thought I would go to Mr. Gaines' funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你...\NThat's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.27,0:09:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}考虑得真周到\Nthoughtful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我回来后帮你干活\NI'll do some work when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你之后会回家  待上一段时间吗\NSo, you're coming home, then, and staying for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是这么打算的\NI plan to, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.81,0:09:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想借...借点钱买东西\NI need to borrow some -- some money for some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:09:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}多少\NHow much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}50块就够了\N$50 will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我找到工作后就还给你\NI'll pay you back when I get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这个我不担心\NI'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一旦我开始工作\NAnd once I start working,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我可能还要买辆二手车开...\NI-I-I might even buy an old beater truck or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你肯定会赚到钱买车的\NI could see you in one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.66,0:10:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你  你怎么过去\NHow -- how are you gonna get there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想走路过去\NI thought I'd walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}开车去吧\NTake the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不想一直开你的车  母亲\NI don't want to keep taking your car, mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.22,0:10:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不想让你走路过去  丹尼尔\NI don't want you to walk, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}开吧\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}注意安全\NBe careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}卢瑟福生前是我的挚友\NRutherford was a good friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他思想敏锐\NHad a sharp mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}特别会打桥牌\NHe played a spirited game of bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不过高尔夫打得不怎样\NWasn't much on the golf course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他打高尔夫就像是出于义务或者去忏悔的\NHe just kind of did that out of obligation or penance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.07,0:11:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道他是位伟大的父亲\NI know that he was a great father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们会想念他\NWe'll miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我的天哪\NHoly mother of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道自己上来说几句话\NI-I'm not sure if it's appropriate for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是不是合适\Nfor me to say something or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}当然  我这样确实讽刺\NThe irony of it doesn't escape me, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}总而言之\NAnyway, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}盖恩斯先生在我离开的那段时间里经常送书给我\NMr. Gaines used to send me books when I was away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.29,0:11:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}单单是法国大革命的书就给我送了三本\NThree books on the French revolution alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他应该喜欢革命  尤其是失败的革命\NHe liked revolutions, I guess, especially failed ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.68,0:12:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我发现那些书都贯穿着同一个主题\NI discovered a theme running through those books --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那就是  人会看到想看的\NThat men will see what they want to see
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}相信想相信的\Nand believe what they want to believe
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}并且为自己的信念浴血奋战\Nand fight to the death for those beliefs,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不论多么误入歧途  多么无望\Nno matter how misguided or hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.43,0:12:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我经常做梦梦到革命\NOftentimes I would dream on these events,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}梦到人群占领街道广场\Nof the crowds taking the streets, taking the squares,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}恐惧在人群中蔓延\Nand the contagion of menacing fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}仁慈为人们所不齿\Nand mercy be damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}偶尔我会...\NAnd occasionally, I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.70,0:12:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会看到盖恩斯先生  置身人群之外\NI would see Mr. Gaines, away from the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}和他目光相汇\NCatch his eye and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你会明白在这群疯狂陶醉的人面前\Nunderstand just how difficult it is
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}两个人的目光要汇集到一起\Nfor two people to come together
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.87,0:12:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是一件多么艰难的事\Nin the face of such intoxicating lunacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}事实上  我不认识盖恩斯先生\NTruth is, I didn't know Mr. Gaines.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}算不上认识\NNot really.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.08,0:13:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他随书附写的便条从来不涉及个人私事\NHis notes that accompanied the books were never personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只是谈谈身边发生的事儿\NThey just talked of the subject matter at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.04,0:13:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}起初我不在意他是否附加那些便条\NAt first I didn't care if he sent them or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.97,0:13:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但是我都看了\NBut I read them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他一直寄\NAnd he kept sending them
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.34,0:13:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}寄了19年\Nfor 19 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就像我说的\NLike I said, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.53,0:13:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道我为什么来这儿\NI don't know why I'm here exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想理由可能是\NI suppose it might reason that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.51,0:13:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我为他穿上这身葬礼服是因为\N...I dressed up for him because on more than one occasion...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他不止一次为我这么做过\N...he dressed up for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谢谢大家\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他到底在搞什么\NWhat the hell was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.76,0:13:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}无耻  厚颜无耻\NGall. Pure gall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那你觉得他能接受这份认罪协议了吗\NSo, you think this plea deal is gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.47,0:14:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我认为她希望如此\NI think she wants it to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.35,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她就能摆脱困扰了\NGet it out of her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}从一开始我就不应该支持那个贱人\NI never should have backed that bitch in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你觉得他会接受认罪协议吗\NYou think he'll take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}霍顿吗\NHolden? Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.80,0:14:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谁知道他会怎么做\NWho knows what he'll do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他能容忍别人尿他身上呢\NHe let a man piss on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.23,0:14:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}乔治·梅尔顿到底去哪儿了  卡尔\NWhere is George goddamn Melton, Carl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你确定要找他吗\NAre you sure you want to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但你仍然把霍顿视为威胁\NBut you still see Holden as a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对谁的威胁\NTo who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对社会\NThe community.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不愿意和他做邻居\NI wouldn't want to live next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你愿意吗\NWould you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你有什么事瞒着我吗  卡尔\NYou keeping secrets from me, Carl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.72,0:14:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}野花和咖啡\NWildflowers and coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:14:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}老天\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.63,0:15:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不得不承认  霍顿可真有创意\NHolden's creative. I'll give him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}问题是小泰不愿意起诉\NProblem is, Ted Jr. won't press charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那我们必须给这小子讲讲道理\NWell, then we just got to talk some sense into that boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.82,0:15:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你手上都有两起勒晕和性侵的案子了\NYou got two choke-outs and two sexual assaults.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你认为这是一个巧合吗\NYou think that's a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}所以我才我提起这件事\NThat's why I brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是作案手法  卡尔\NIt's modus operandi, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.74,0:15:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这真是天赐良机\NIt's a gift from the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}它能把认罪协议这种无稽之谈扼杀在摇篮里\NIt'll nip this plea-deal nonsense in the bud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我从法律角度跟小泰谈过了\NI discussed the legal side with Ted Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.74,0:15:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他说他不想这件事令他尴尬\NSaid he doesn't want the embarrassment of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}而且对此情绪非常激烈\NFelt pretty strong about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我对他的小情绪无能为力\NI can't help his little feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}霍顿把咖啡豆塞进他屁眼时事情就无法改变了\NThe die was cast when Holden shoved coffee beans up his ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}议员先生  要续杯吗\NHey. Refill, Senator?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}怎么不叫我"亲爱的"了\NWhat happened to calling me "Sweetie"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}亲爱的  续杯吗\NRefill, sweetie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真听话\NAttagirl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是咖啡渣  罗兰\NIt was grounds, Roland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-什么  -不是咖啡豆  是咖啡渣\N- What? - Not beans. Grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.81,0:15:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}小泰说他并没有真塞\NAnd Teddy said there wasn't actual penetration.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.00,0:15:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我才不管有没有真塞\NI don't give a good God damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你跟我说没有一个检察官\NYou tell me any backwoods prosecutor
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}能说服陪审团相信他是蓄意的\Ncouldn't convince a jury that that was the intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他肯定不会真的都给他硬塞进去啊\NHe damn sure wasn't making sand castles back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.71,0:16:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们得找小泰做笔录\NWe just got to get Junior on the record.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他不会乐意的\NHe ain't gonna like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}肯定不会\NNot one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这件事比他重要  卡尔\NWell, this is bigger than him, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这件事比我们所有人都重要\NThis is bigger than all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你告诉我这件事是对的\NYou did the right thing telling me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.11,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}现在别给我怂了\NDon't go soft on me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}8美元的饭付60美元吗\N$60 on an $8 meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}今晚去你那儿方便吗\NYou up for a little visit later?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}今晚我儿子在  议员先生\NGot my son tonight, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你搅得一位老人家心神不宁了\NYou're messing with an old man's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}所以你才会继续回来找我啊\NThat's why you keep coming back for more.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}别笑了\NStop laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}保持一步一步往前走就好\NJust keep one foot in front of the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}乔恩\NJon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}乔恩\NJon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-没事了  -你又一次死里逃生\N- Okay. - You've escaped death once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是家族遗传\NIt's in the family DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}霍顿家族不可战胜  是吧\NHoldens are invincible, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.29,0:17:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都是超级英雄\NSuperheroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}先生们  贴近你身边的女士\NMen, bring your ladies close.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.13,0:17:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}情侣舞时间到了\NIt's time for a couples dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我喜欢你  乔恩·斯特恩\NI like you, Jon Stern.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们应该确定关系吗\NShould we go steady?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你为什么不闭嘴直接吻我\NWhy don't you shut up and kiss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}当着所有人面吗\NIn front of all of Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不在乎谁看着我们\NI don't care who sees us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.27,0:18:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不敢相信你就要走了\NI can't believe you're about to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.52,0:18:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就几天而已\NFor a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}死囚牢在向你招手\NDeath row beckons?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会回来的\NI'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}然后你会再离开\NAnd then you'll leave again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们不必非得如此吧\NDoesn't have to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.69,0:18:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}能至少给我一份分别礼物吗\NDo I at least get a parting gift?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.49,0:18:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}抱歉打扰了\NExcuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}首先你哥哥在盖恩斯先生的葬礼上出现\NFirst your brother shows up at Mr. Gaines' funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不知道胡言乱语什么\Nrambling about God knows what,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}现在你们在这儿的行为就像...\Nand now here you are acting like...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我明白你必须过自己的生活\NI know you have to live your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我理解这点\NI understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我明白你的处境不是你的错\NI know it's not your fault, the position you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.61,0:18:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但是你们能去别处这样做吗  拜托\NBut could you go do it somewhere else, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这样我们就能不去想汉娜\NSo that we don't have to think about Hanna
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.29,0:18:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}以及那晚她的遭遇\Nand what happened to her that night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那时你多大\NHow old were you then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:18:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}5岁\N5?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.46,0:19:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-乔恩  不要  -不  说真的\N- Jon, please. - No. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.51,0:19:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}8岁\N8?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.01,0:19:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我那时年纪够大了\NI was old enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}足够大干什么\NOld enough. For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}听你的父母告诉你那些事\NTo listen to what your parents told you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}因为他们说的是真的而深信不疑吗\Nand believe it because they said it was true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}害怕自己动脑子想想吗\NAfraid to think for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}害怕看到所有事实真相吗\NScared to look at all the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.28,0:19:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}为什么这样\NAnd for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这样你才永远不必承认\NSo you'd never have to admit to yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你自己也许是错的\Nthat you might be wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你能去别处这样做吗\NCould you go do that somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}拜托了\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}晚安\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}祝你好运\NAnd good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔在盖恩斯的葬礼上胡言乱语了吗\NDaniel was rambling at Gaines' funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.60,0:19:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}而我们在溜冰场上纵情欢愉\NAnd here we are, living it up at the skating rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对世事漠不关心\NNot a care in the damn world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们早就该注意的\NWe should have known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我早该注意的\NI should have known better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没关系的  乔恩\NIt's okay, Jon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.05,0:19:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我是说  去她的  管她撞见什么呢\NI mean, screw her and the minivan she came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们要担心的不是她\NIt's not her we should be worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你说得对\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}差点忘了\NAlmost forgot for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}蓝药丸  白药丸\NBlue pill, white pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.72,0:20:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}蓝药丸  白药丸\NBlue pill, white pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}蓝药丸  白药丸\NBlue pill, white pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}蓝药丸  白药丸\NBlue pill, white pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.43,0:20:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}蓝药丸  白药丸\NBlue pill, white pill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.18,0:20:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔\NDaniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.18,0:20:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我叫查理\NMy name's Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是你找我吗\NDid you call for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我没找你\NI didn't call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我是牧师\NI'm the chaplain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}赞美上帝\NPraise God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}什么\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}如果你想说话  我就在这儿\NI'm here if you want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.73,0:20:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不想说话\NI don't want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那你介意我就坐在这儿吗\NYou mind if I just sit here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你做什么随便你\NI don't care what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}牧师查理\NCharlie the chaplain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}牧师查理\NCharlie chaplain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.67,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你反射弧够长的\NTook you long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我头脑不像以前那么敏锐了\NI'm not as sharp as I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这样对你来说会更好些吗\NDoes that work better for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不像以前那么敏锐会更好些吗\Nnot being as sharp as you used to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.73,0:21:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}闭嘴  查理牧师\NShut up, Charlie chaplain.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我没什么别的意思\NI'm not making a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只是问问\NJust asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.53,0:21:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我更希望你待在默片时代\NI liked you better in the silent era.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:50.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这个厨房早就该装修了\NThis kitchen is long overdue for a remodel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.43,0:21:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道妈妈很兴奋\NI know mom's psyched.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你真是个敏感的人  杰瑞德\NYou're a sensitive person, Jared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是个很好的特点\NIt's a good trait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}妈妈说警方\NMom said that the Sheriff's department
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}退回了一些我的个人物品\Nreturned some of my possessions from the, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我的随身听和一些其它东西\Nmy walkman and other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}其他东西我都找到了  就是没找到随身听\NI found the other items, but I-I didn't find my walkman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想我会找到它的\NI'm sure it'll turn up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那是名里有个Z的莱斯利\NWell, that'll be Lezley with a "Z."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.83,0:22:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我该走了\NBetter go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔\NDaniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}怎么了  杰瑞德\NYes, Jared?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.75,0:22:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你知道今天是什么日子吧\ND -- you know what today is, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们亲爱的母亲的生日\NThe day of our dear mother's birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}派对两点开始\N2:00 is the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.79,0:23:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会到的\NI'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}汉娜当时还只是个孩子\NHanna was just a baby back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.53,0:23:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但我当时并没有那么想她\NI didn't think of her that way at the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.73,0:23:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}也许因为我也只是个孩子吧\NI guess 'cause we were all just babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有好奇心是好事  杰瑞德\NIt's good to be curious about things, Jared...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}尤其是对禁忌之事\NEspecially when those things are somehow taboo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只是要\NYou just got to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.31,0:23:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}小心\Ncareful.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.87,0:23:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}钱给我\NGive me the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你就拿着微波炉和摩尔炖肉\NNow, you get the microwave and the dinty moore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.95,0:24:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}事情我来谈\Nand let me do the talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.85,0:24:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}塔特  我是莱斯利\NTater, it's Lezley.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.76,0:24:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谁\NWho?
