Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.03,0:36:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但该死  万一你经受不住痛苦呢\NBut, damn, if you ain't got a high threshold.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.54,0:36:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}后会有期  伙计\NSee you around the fringes, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.65,0:36:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我现在该去哪儿  莱斯利\NSo, where to now, Lezley?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.91,0:36:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就在你的身后\NMight ought to go look behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.29,0:36:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}家让我害怕\NI'm afraid to.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.15,0:36:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.01,0:36:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}换做我也是\NI would be, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.59,0:37:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是个用完即抛的社会\NI mean, it's a throwaway society.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.86,0:37:26.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没错\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.30,0:37:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们买了东西  然后再丢掉\NI mean, we buy stuff, and then we throw it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.05,0:37:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}还不如借呢\NI mean, why not lease it
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.59,0:37:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}使完后再还回去呢\Nand then give it back when we're done, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.52,0:37:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}让他们把东西送去垃圾场处理\NLet them haul it off to the landfill.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.75,0:37:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}说得好\NGood point.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.68,0:37:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没错\NDamn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.78,0:37:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你好  托妮\NHello, Tawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.00,0:37:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你好  丹尼尔\NHello, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.65,0:37:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你看起来很平静\NYou look restful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.26,0:37:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我感觉很平静\NI feel restful.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.67,0:37:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.53,0:37:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你呢\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.17,0:38:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你感觉怎么样\NHow are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.17,0:38:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我...\NWell, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.31,0:38:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我心中百感交集\NI'm feeling a lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.78,0:38:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但肯定不平静\Nbut, uh, I wouldn't say restful is one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.36,0:38:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}托妮  谢谢你\NWell...Thank you, Tawney, for, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.29,0:38:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那天帮了我\Nreach out for me on that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.85,0:38:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我希望我做得对  丹尼尔\NI hope I did the right thing, Daniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.23,0:38:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我觉得你做得对\NI think you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.27,0:38:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你触动我心扉  托妮\NYou made me feel, Tawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.46,0:38:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真真切切  你懂吗\NReally feel, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.33,0:38:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}懂\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.08,0:38:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我很久没被触动了\NFor the first time in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.59,0:39:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这才是人之本性  不是吗\NThat's a big part of what makes us human, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.76,0:39:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是的\NI think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.34,0:39:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我觉得这会\NI think it...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.04,0:39:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}让内心变得丰满\Ndeepens us.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.61,0:39:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我觉得内心丰满了不少\NI've been deepened.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.61,0:39:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们过会儿就得走了\NWe're gonna have to scoot here in a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.28,0:39:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我问问托妮\NSee what Tawn--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.07,0:39:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}各位\NHey, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.70,0:39:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我要宣布一个消息\NI,h, got an announcement to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.79,0:39:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}宝贝  你能过来下吗\NH-hey, uh, baby, would you come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.01,0:39:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}来  宝贝\NCome here, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.68,0:39:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}妈妈  我们还有个礼物要送你\NMom, we got one more present for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.48,0:39:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她怀孕了\NWe're pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.63,0:39:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}什么  天呐\NWhat?! Oh, my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.39,0:39:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-惊喜吧  -托妮\N- Surprise! - Tawney!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.09,0:39:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}生日快乐\NHappy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.56,0:40:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-这是个好消息  儿子  -谢谢  爸爸\N- That's good news, son. - Aw, thanks, dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.84,0:40:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我为你们俩高兴\NI'm happy for you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.61,0:40:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}太棒了\NOh, that's just wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.10,0:40:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道我本该保密\NI know I wasn't supposed to say anything, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.49,0:40:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但我迫不及待了\Nbut I just -- I just couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.09,0:40:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就是等不及了\NJust couldn't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.74,0:40:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}天呐\NOh, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.98,0:40:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这里面有个小家伙了\NThere's a bun in that oven, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.65,0:40:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}恭喜  泰德\NCongratulations, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.29,0:40:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-谢了  乔恩  -恭喜\N- Thanks, Jon. - Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.84,0:40:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}乔恩和我也要宣布一件事\NJon and I have an announcement, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.03,0:40:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}星期二  我去了梅肯的一家临终关怀医院\NOn Tuesday, I go to this hospice in Macon.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.97,0:40:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你是个圣人\NYou're a saint, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.90,0:40:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那里有人去世\NThey're just people dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.92,0:40:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}每天都会发生\NHappens every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.93,0:41:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我要死了\NAm I dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.45,0:41:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你想死吗  丹尼尔\NDo you want to die, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.45,0:41:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我妹妹总插手我的事\NMy sister keeps interfering.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.85,0:41:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你说清楚点\NYou're mumbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.48,0:41:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她长大了  爱管闲事\NShe's a little busybody, all grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.97,0:41:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不管怎样\NAnyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.45,0:41:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我为他们放音乐\NI play music for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.45,0:41:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有时候我也只能放放音乐了\NSometimes that's all I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.19,0:41:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}言语和音乐相比黯然失色\NWords can pale in comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.60,0:41:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你说得话肯定比不上\NYours sure do.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.07,0:41:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对一些人来说\NWell, for some...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.64,0:41:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}音乐是唯一能让他们安然入眠的东西\NIt's the only thing that will let them sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.42,0:41:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}给予他们慰藉\NIt's the only thing that gives them solace.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.76,0:41:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你有多久没听音乐了  丹尼尔\NHow long has it been since you've heard music, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.14,0:42:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}美终将救赎世界\NBeauty will redeem the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.83,0:42:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你是个傻瓜  查理\NYou're a fool, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.55,0:43:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔\NDaniel.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.66,0:43:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔\NDaniel.
